# hexa-lang /.raw — L0 universal (19 rules)
# SSOT — 이 파일이 전부. 새 세션 인지 없이도 위반 불가, low-level enforcement 전용.
# 포맷 스펙: self/raw_loader.hexa
#
# 포맷:
#   raw <num> <status> "<name>"
#     <key> <value...>
#     ...
#   (빈 줄 = rule 구분, #… = 주석, 같은 key 여러 줄 = 배열)
#
# status (5, 잠금): live warn new deferred convention
# key whitelist (15, 잠금):
#   slug enforce decl scope opt-out base since why note bans
#   defer-until follow-up promoted-at proof method
#
# 필수: enforce (능동 rule), 또는 status=deferred + defer-until + why (보류 rule)
# slug: stable identifier — 외부 참조는 `raw:<slug>` 형식. 번호(num) shift 에 불변. 순서 변경 잦음 → 참조 금지, slug 만 사용.
# 주: git-hook 은 전면 폐기 (2026-04-19). enforcement = raw:os-lock chflags uchg (kernel EPERM) + manual/CI 호출.

raw 0 live ".raw + .own — project root SSOT (파생 없음)"
  slug root-ssot
  enforce tool/root_ssot_check.hexa
  decl .raw .own
  scope 모든 하위 rule 의 기원 — .ext/.roadmap/.loop 는 여기서 파생
  why 이 2 파일이 프로젝트 진리원. 소실 = 복구 불가 (타 SSOT 는 재생성 가능). raw:os-lock 은 파일 단위 lock 기법 (L0 대체, 개별파일), 본 rule 은 의미론 root 선언.
  proof tool/root_ssot_check.hexa

raw 1 live "os-level file lock — all raw + .own (chflags uchg)"
  slug os-lock
  enforce tool/os_level_lock.hexa
  method chflags uchg (Darwin) / chattr +i (Linux)
  scope all raw rules (.raw) + .own + .ext + .roadmap + .loop + raw:ai-tool-ban grandfather bans
  why pre-commit and PreToolUse hooks are bypassable. Kernel EPERM is the only real enforcement. All rule declarations live in .raw and all project directives in .own — locking these files = locking every downstream rule.
  proof tool/os_level_lock.hexa verify
  note chflags nouchg requires explicit unlock by owner. Any write attempt in-session returns EPERM. `./hx edit <file>` is the audited unlock/relock path.
  note level tiering — required (5 SSOT) at L1 uchg minimum; .raw .own promotable to L2 schg via `./hx harden` (sudo). raw:ai-tool-ban grandfathers at L1.

raw 2 live "self-format — .raw/.own/.ext 은 본 문법을 만족"
  slug self-format
  enforce self/raw_cli.hexa#verify
  decl self/raw_loader.hexa
  proof self/raw_cli.hexa
  keys ['slug','enforce','decl','scope','opt-out','base','since','why','note','bans','defer-until','follow-up','promoted-at','proof','method','mode','ttl','keys','statuses-rule','statuses-roadmap','statuses-loop']
  statuses-rule ['live','warn','new','deferred','convention']
  statuses-roadmap ['planned','active','done','blocked','deferred']
  statuses-loop ['live','paused','new','convention','deferred']
  why SSOT 가 자기 spec 을 어기면 모든 하위 rule 무효. 파싱 에러 = commit reject. 배열풀은 이 rule 에만 — 코드는 slug:self-format 참조만 (중복 금지).

raw 3 warn "ai-native 24 @attr 사용"
  slug attr-usage
  enforce tool/ai_native_scan.hexa
  decl self/ai_native/ai_native.json
  note block 승격은 Tier 2/3 semantic 분석 후 (false-positive 위험)

raw 4 deferred "ai-native 알고리즘 (O(2^n)→O(n))"
  slug ai-native-algo
  decl self/ai_native/ai_native_enforcement_progress.json#algorithm_whitelist
  defer-until 2026-10
  why 의미론 판단 필요 — 섣부른 enforcement 는 false-positive. hexa-lang AI-native 대치 성숙 후.

raw 5 live "@attr 네이밍"
  slug attr-naming
  enforce self/attrs/_registry.hexa#check_naming_all
  decl self/attrs/_naming.hexa
  proof self/attrs/_registry.hexa

raw 6 live "폴더명 (F4 generic_dir)"
  slug folder-naming
  enforce tool/ai_native_scan.hexa#F4
  bans utils helpers common lib misc stuff base
  proof tool/ai_native_scan.hexa

raw 7 live "트리구조 (F5 loner + F6 parent-child)"
  slug tree-structure
  enforce tool/ai_native_scan.hexa#F5,F6
  proof tool/ai_native_scan.hexa
  note F5 = 단일 파일만 있는 디렉토리, F6 = parent/parent_child.hexa 중복

raw 8 live "파일명 (F1 version + F2 stage/phase + F3 temp)"
  slug file-naming
  enforce tool/ai_native_scan.hexa#F1,F2,F3
  bans _v\d+ stage p\d _old _new _bak _tmp
  proof tool/ai_native_scan.hexa

raw 9 live "HEXA-ONLY (.rs/.toml/.py/.sh 금지)"
  slug hexa-only
  enforce tool/hexa_only_lint.hexa
  decl doc/hexa_lang_breakthroughs.json#HX4
  bans .rs .toml .py .sh
  proof tool/hexa_only_lint.hexa
  follow-up tool/hexa_only_lint.hexa 구현 — 기존 git-hook 인라인 grep 로직 (staged file 확장자 스캔) 의 hexa 포팅

raw 10 live "proof-carrying mark (선언 vs 현실 매치)"
  slug proof-carrying
  enforce tool/drift_scanner.hexa
  decl anima roadmap_drift_audit 2026-04-18
  proof tool/drift_scanner.hexa
  why anima roadmap 136 phases 전부 done 선언 → 실제 22 unwired + 3 FALSIFIED + 9 drifts. 선언 자체에 증거 강제.

raw 11 live "AI-native 원칙 강제 (default-on)"
  slug ai-native-enforce
  enforce tool/ai_native_lint.hexa#default-strict
  decl doc/ai-native.md
  opt-out #!hexa lax
  base .hexa-lax-baseline
  proof tool/ai_native_lint.hexa
  why strict 명시 드물어 실효 0 → opt-in → opt-out 역전. drift 같은 법 어긴 코드 자가 작성 방지.

raw 12 warn "silent error 금지 (exit/empty-catch)"
  slug silent-error
  enforce tool/error_propagation_lint.hexa
  decl self/raws/silent_error.hexa
  opt-out @allow-silent-exit
  proof self/raws/silent_error.hexa
  why 2026-04-18 ROI #149 fix(import) deep use-chain silent exit = Claude default drift. raw:proof-carrying 과 대칭 (done=proof, fail=message).
  follow-up let _ = f() on error-return 탐지 — 타입 정보 필요 (Tier 2, deferred)
  follow-up block 승격 — 354 violation triage (@allow-silent-exit 일괄 vs err msg rewrite) 완료 후
  follow-up hexa_stage0 preflight induce_all() 통합 — 현재는 explicit manual 호출만 (git-hook 전면 폐기 2026-04-19)

raw 13 new "ai-tool and git-hook config ban"
  slug ai-tool-ban
  enforce tool/ai_tool_ban_lint.hexa
  bans CLAUDE.md AGENTS.md CODEX.md .cursorrules .cursor .windsurfrules .aider.conf.yml .continuerules .github/copilot-instructions.md .claude
  bans .git/hooks tool/hooks .githooks .husky
  why SSOT = .raw + .own only. Ban every AI-tool config layer (md files, hooks, skills) AND every git-hook layer (pre-commit scripts, husky, githooks dir). 2026-04-19: grandfather removed — all existing git-hook files deleted. raw:os-lock (chflags uchg) is the real enforcement — OS EPERM is the gate; enforce scripts are manual/CI-invoked only.
  proof tool/ai_tool_ban_lint.hexa

raw 14 new "외부자원 선언 — .ext SSOT"
  slug ext-ssot
  enforce tool/ext_lint.hexa
  decl .ext
  scope ssh-host / api-endpoint / external-binary / service / submodule
  why 외부 의존 (hetzner SSH, Anthropic API, Docker pod, git submodule 등) 난립 차단. 감사/복구/오프라인 실행 위한 명시적 선언.
  proof tool/ext_lint.hexa
  follow-up ext_lint.hexa 구현 — .ext 파서 (raw_loader 재활용) + 필드 검증 (kind whitelist + endpoint reachability stub)

raw 15 live "no hardcoding — values belong in SSOT"
  slug no-hardcode
  enforce tool/no_hardcode_lint.hexa
  scope magic numbers, paths, URLs, hostnames, credentials, API keys, version strings, tuning constants, timeouts
  opt-out @const (named constant with reason) + .hardcode-baseline (grandfather drift)
  why Hardcoded values hide the source of truth and fossilize assumptions. Relocate to .ext (external resource), .own (project rule), or named const with @const marker. Unexplained literals = invisible contract.
  proof tool/no_hardcode_lint.hexa
  follow-up no_hardcode_lint.hexa implementation — literal scanner + whitelist (0, 1, -1, empty string, small bounds in hot kernels) + .hardcode-baseline grandfather list

raw 16 new "roadmap SSOT — .roadmap"
  slug roadmap-ssot
  enforce tool/roadmap_lint.hexa
  decl .roadmap
  scope phase / track / milestone / ETA / owner declarations
  why Roadmap sprawl previously scattered across ad-hoc .json / .md files + memory notes. One SSOT at repo root with declarative directive format. Supports raw:proof-carrying (phase=done requires proof).
  proof tool/roadmap_lint.hexa
  follow-up parser extension — add `roadmap` kind to self/raw_loader.hexa _fmt_is_header_token.

raw 17 new "loop SSOT — .loop"
  slug loop-ssot
  enforce tool/loop_lint.hexa
  decl .loop
  scope recurring tasks (interval-based /loop, cron, ScheduleWakeup, RemoteTrigger)
  why Hidden cron/loop entries scattered across ~/.claude, tmux sessions, ad-hoc scripts. Single audit point for "what runs on a schedule against this repo". raw:ai-tool-ban bans ~/.claude hooks → recurring tasks must surface here.
  proof tool/loop_lint.hexa
  follow-up parser extension — add `loop` kind. interval field validator (duration or cron syntax).

raw 18 new "self-host fixpoint convergence"
  slug self-host-fixpoint
  enforce tool/verify_fixpoint.hexa
  decl tool/fixpoint_v3_v4.hexa
  scope v2→v3 byte-identical + v3→v4 stable
  why bootstrap 폐쇄 (Rust/C 의존 제거) 궁극 목표. fixpoint 없이 self-host 미완결. .roadmap#9 active 를 실제 enforce 로 묶는다.
  proof tool/p7_7_fixpoint_check.hexa
  follow-up status new → live 승격은 v4 달성 후 (ROI #153 close 후)
  follow-up ROI #152 (hexa_v2 circular rebuild regression) close 전까지는 --live 모드 불가. 기본 scaffold 보고만.
